<para>represents a box in 3D space subdivided on voxels stored in T; and stores minimum and maximum values among all valid voxels Generated from class <computeroutput>MR::SimpleVolumeMinMaxU16</computeroutput>. Base classes: Direct: (non-virtual) <computeroutput>MR::SimpleVolumeU16</computeroutput> <computeroutput>MR::Box&lt;unsigned short&gt;</computeroutput> Supported <computeroutput><ref refid="common_8h_1ac983b89bddb9b22c9b416f31399f0095" kindref="member">MR_PassBy</ref></computeroutput> modes: <computeroutput>MR_PassBy_DefaultConstruct</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>MR_PassBy_Copy</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>MR_PassBy_Move</computeroutput> (and <computeroutput>MR_PassBy_DefaultArgument</computeroutput> and <computeroutput>MR_PassBy_NoObject</computeroutput> if supported by the callee). </para>
        </detaileddescription>
